{"tid":2276593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登發表勝利演說：這是美國療傷的時候 賀錦麗：拜登是團結者","createTime":"2020-11-08T02:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T02:35:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a78eb18fd63a766facab47f5c47c6fd09a2a1c8d","tid":2276593,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"●拜登的演說以尋求和解為主，指出「我承諾不尋求分化，而是團結」，更向支持現任總統特朗普的人拋出友誼之手，「我明白你們感到失望，我也曾兩次參選總統失敗，但給我們彼此一個機會吧」。拜登稱，人們重新應聆聽彼此的聲音，「我們不能再視對手為敵人，他們不是我們的敵人，他們是美國人」，「這是美國人療傷的時候」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201108/TG27OFYVBNAP3DDJKRJE4RLT7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201108%2FTG27OFYVBNAP3DDJKRJE4RLT7Q%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft2yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=d1c3c5de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201108%2FTG27OFYVBNAP3DDJKRJE4RLT7Q%2F&h=4df2f990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201108/TG27OFYVBNAP3DDJKRJE4RLT7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"2a7b5d6b781fbf5fa92452105ed5325ce7376853","tid":2276593,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T02:32:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47f9412b7bbca3344009f680405e7e4bf0fb3b66","tid":2276593,"uid":375706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"過多兩年到我上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda7e64efe42ccfc9216e7263c54ea489ba201fd","tid":2276593,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T02:35:37.000Z","msg":"會更加撕裂"}]}